Company Description                    




                        LG Display Co., Ltd manufactures digital display products using TFT-LCD (Thin Film Transistor Liquid Crystal Display), LTPS LCD and AMOLED technologies. The company's products include LCD TVs, Public Display, monitor, notebook and mobile phones. LG Display have 2 plant facilities located in Paju and Gumi, South Korea.
LG Display was formerly known as Geumsung Software and changed its name to LG Display Co., Ltd. in March 2008. The company was founded in 1985.                     


